text: ql -ayha alrswl- llyhwd walnsara: 'iinakum lastum ealaa hzz min aldiyn ma dumtum lm temlu bima fi altawrat wal'injyl, wama ja'akum bih muhamad min alqran, wa'iina kthyrana min 'ahl alkitab la yaziduhum 'inzal alquran 'iilayk 'iilaa tjbburana wjhwdana, fahum yhsdwnk; li'ana allah bethk bhdhh alrisalat alkhatmt, alty bayan fiha meaybhm, fala tahzan -ayha alrswl- ealaa tkdhybhm lk
